["<div dir=\"rtl\" align=\"right\">\n <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: -52.65pt\" dir=\"rtl\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"24\">\n   إِنَّكَ فِي دَارٍ لَهَا مُدَّةٌ\n   </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"24\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"24\">\n   يُقْبَلُ فِيهَا عَمَلُ الْعَامِلِ‏\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"24\">\n   أَلَا تَرَى الْمَوْتَ مُحِيطاً بِهَا\n   </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"24\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"24\">\n   يُكْذَبُ فِيهَا أَمَلُ الْآمِلِ‏\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n    <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   تُعَجِّلُ الذَّنْبَ لِمَا تَشْتَهِي‏\n     </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   وَ تَأْمُلُ التَّوْبَةَ فِي قَابِلٍ‏\n     </td>\n  </tr>\n    <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"22\">\n   وَ الْمَوْتُ يَأْتِي أَهْلَهُ بَغْتَةً\n   </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"22\">\n   &nbsp;</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"22\">\n   مَا ذَاكَ فِعْلَ الْحَازِمِ الْعَاقِلِ‏\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n      </table>\n  \n</div>\n","عيون أخبار الرضا  ج 2 ص 176"]